</em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"f75549e3fbfe8897a9b996a0fdb49ce9e3aa059d","tid":1668013,"uid":313362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"Twitter Verification Call個電話語音驗證係6位數<br />\n我試到俾佢block咗去google先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係twitter 123456 twitter 123456 twitter 123456<br />\n屌佢讀到twenty咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://ukkkoshi.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-53.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fukkkoshi.blog.fc2.com%2Fblog-entry-53.html&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=91c4b349\" target=\"_blank\">http://ukkkoshi.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-53.html</a>"}]}